Configure JTAG debugging for {{device_type}}.

Target: {{target_chip}}
Interface: {{jtag_interface}}
Debug Speed: {{debug_speed}} kHz

Setup Steps:
1. Configure OpenOCD for {{target_chip}}
2. Set JTAG interface to {{jtag_interface}}
3. Set adapter speed to {{debug_speed}} kHz
4. Initialize flash programming support
5. Configure GDB server on port {{gdb_port}}

OpenOCD Configuration:
```
interface {{jtag_interface}}
adapter speed {{debug_speed}}
source [find target/{{target_chip}}.cfg]
gdb_port {{gdb_port}}
```

